<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 01:13:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着新钱包抽签通知，Polymarket 伊朗赌注达到 5.29 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/polymarket-iran-bets-hit-529-million-as-new-wallets-draw-notice</link><description>随着美国和以色列的炸弹本周末落在伊朗身上，Polymarket 上的投注者（其中与袭击时间相关的合同交易额达 5.29 亿美元）开始获利。区块链侦探几乎立即开始在最近的投注中寻找不寻常的模式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.fUiA15VPBE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 21:24:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/polymarket-iran-bets-hit-529-million-as-new-wallets-draw-notice</guid></item><item><title>美国和以色列袭击伊朗后比特币跌破 64,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</link><description>在美国和以色列周六开始袭击伊朗各地的目标后，比特币和其他加密货币大幅下跌，引发了高风险资产的连锁反应。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idqJtRSUh1hc/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 07:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</guid></item><item><title>由于人工智能担心扰乱市场，比特币跌至 65,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/bitcoin-sinks-towards-65-000-as-inflation-douses-risk-appetite</link><description>周五，由于投资者担心持续通胀、人工智能干扰以及与私人信贷相关的问题，投资者纷纷撤离风险较高的资产，比特币跌回 65,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iXz9PcgQVV8M/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 15:17:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/bitcoin-sinks-towards-65-000-as-inflation-douses-risk-appetite</guid></item><item><title>西班牙推动 2028 年推出数字欧元以遏制对美国的依赖</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/spain-pushes-for-2028-launch-of-digital-euro-to-curb-us-reliance</link><description>西班牙希望数字欧元在 2028 年成为现实——比其官方目标日期早一年，一些人已经认为这个目标非常雄心勃勃。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iE1LTdgrJVLg/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 15:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/spain-pushes-for-2028-launch-of-digital-euro-to-curb-us-reliance</guid></item><item><title>在线经纪商 XTB 表示波兰的加密货币僵局有扩大的风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/online-broker-xtb-says-poland-s-crypto-gridlock-risks-expansion</link><description>快速增长的交易平台 XTB SA 表示，其扩张计划面临波兰监管加密资产政治僵局的风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWkvQEPhSiqg/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 13:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/online-broker-xtb-says-poland-s-crypto-gridlock-risks-expansion</guid></item><item><title>英国赌博监管机构将考虑允许投注者使用加密货币支付</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/uk-gambling-watchdog-to-weigh-allowing-punters-to-pay-in-crypto</link><description>随着英国逐步采用数字资产法规，英国赌博委员会计划探索允许赌徒用加密货币支付赌注。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isPu3Z9WkJ9g/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 11:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/uk-gambling-watchdog-to-weigh-allowing-punters-to-pay-in-crypto</guid></item></channel></rss>